data.description: Wonderful opportunity to own a beautiful 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home located in the desirable Mystic at Mariners Village community! This two story move-in ready home provides ample space for your growing family! Through the double entry doors, walk into the foyer with high volume ceilings and tons of natural light and an inviting staircase at the heart of the home. To the left, step down into your cozy living room with oversized windows drawing in the natural light. This room leads you back into the formal dining room located right off the kitchen. The kitchen features floor to ceiling cabinetry, granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances with sliding glass doors leading out back. At the rear of the home is the family room charmed with a wood burning fireplace, perfect for intimate family gatherings. Up the stairs with laminate flooring are the 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The primary bedroom features a beautiful ensuite with a glass front walk-in shower and a rain head shower head. Step out back and enjoy the Florida weather all year round in the fully screen enclosed back porch that leads out onto the concrete pad surrounded by additional green space and mature landscaping.  Roof 2018, repipe and whole house water filtration/softener system 2020, exterior painting 2023, interior painting 2020, gutter guards 2022, backyard concrete pad 2020, Water Heater 2021.  Centrally located in a highly sought-after neighborhood, this home is just minutes away from downtown, major highways, numerous shopping and dining options, the Orlando International Airport and all the major attractions Orlando has to offer.
